<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - VKAcademy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #0056b3;
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #e3f2fd, #bbdefb);
            color: #002855;
        }

            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
                margin: 0 0 10px;
            }

            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.2em;
                margin: 0;
            }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

            .section p {
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

        #map {
            height: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Inspiring Young Minds, Shaping Bright Futures.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="our-story">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>
                Founded in 2024, VKAcademy began with a simple yet powerful vision:
                "To ignite a lifelong love of learning in children, fostering curiosity, confidence, and creativity."
            </p>
            <p>
                From our humble beginnings, we have grown into a trusted platform dedicated
                to empowering young learners and creating a lasting positive impact.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="our-mission">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                At VKAcademy, our mission is simple: to empower children through engaging, meaningful
                learning experiences that inspire growth, curiosity, and a passion for knowledge.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="our-team">
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <p>
                Our team is a group of dedicated professionals passionate about education and
                child development. Together, we bring diverse skills and backgrounds, united by
                a commitment to shaping bright futures.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="why-choose-us">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <p>
                At VKAcademy, we go beyond traditional learning. Our engaging resources are
                designed to nurture children’s natural curiosity, build confidence, and foster
                a love for discovery.
            </p>
            <p>
                Our goal is to provide tools that support lifelong success, helping children
                adapt to an ever-changing world with joy and resilience.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="section" id="location">
            <h2>Our Location</h2>
            <div id="map"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css" />
    <script>
        const map = L.map('map').setView([42.130349, 24.747892], 15);
        L.tileLayer('https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png', {
            maxZoom: 19,
        }).addTo(map);
        L.marker([42.140349, 24.747892])
            .addTo(map)
            .bindPopup('<b>VKAcademy</b><br>ul. "Ivan Vazov" 16, 4000 Plovdiv')
            .openPopup();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
